   233|    'FILES CHANGED:\nNO CODE CHANGED — no development was completed.',
   234|    'COMMANDS RUN:\nNONE — no commands were executed.',
   235|    'TEST RESULT:\nNOT VERIFIED — tests were not run.',
   236|    'TYPECHECK RESULT:\nNOT VERIFIED — typecheck was not run.',
   237|    'STATUS:\nBLOCKED',
   238|    `PROOF:\nBLOCKED — the generated answer ${DEVELOPER_EXECUTION_GUARD_MARKER}:\n${reasons}`,
